Paccayapaccanīyānuloma
Napurejātaduka
503.
1733Napurejātapaccayā hetuyā satta, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā dasa, anantare satta, samanantare satta, sahajāte nava, aññamaññe tīṇi, nissaye nava, upanissaye nava, pacchājāte tīṇi, āsevane tīṇi, kamme satta, vipāke ekaṃ, āhāre satta, indriye satta, jhāne satta, magge satta, sampayutte tīṇi, vippayutte tīṇi, atthiyā nava, natthiyā satta, vigate satta, avigate nava…pe… .
